<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Lost ID Has Been Found! - PataID</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <div style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #25AAE1, #22c55e); padding: 20px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0;">ðŸŽ‰ Great News!</h1>
        <p style="color: white; opacity: 0.8; margin: 5px 0 0;">Your ID has been found</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="padding: 30px; background: #f8fafc;">
        <h2 style="color: #032540;">Hello <%= ownerName %>,</h2>
        
        <p>We're happy to inform you that your lost <strong><%= idType %></strong> has been found!</p>
        
        <div style="background: white; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h3 style="color: #25AAE1; margin-top: 0;">Found ID Details:</h3>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>ID Number:</strong> <%= idNumber %></li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Campus:</strong> <%= campus %></li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Found On:</strong> <%= foundDate %></li>
                <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Found By:</strong> <%= finderType === 'security' ? 'Campus Security' : 'Community Member' %></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>To claim your ID, please click the button below and follow the verification steps:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= reportUrl %>" style="background: #22c55e; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">
                Claim Your ID
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div style="background: #e8f7fc; border-left: 4px solid #25AAE1; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #032540;">ðŸ“‹ What to do next:</h4>
            <ol style="margin: 10px 0;">
                <li>Click the button above to start the claim process</li>
                <li>Verify your identity using one of our secure methods</li>
                <li>Arrange pickup with the finder or security desk</li>
                <li>Bring valid identification when collecting your ID</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact campus security.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div style="background: #032540; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px;">
        <p>&copy; <%= year %> PataID. Reconnecting lost IDs with their owners.</p>
        <p style="opacity: 0.8;">This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>